name: VISHWAS DYAN PRABODHINI & RESEARCH INSTITUTE
briefDescription: We are registered organisation, last 15 yrs we are serving in Nashik and near by area in Maharashtra for Working with youth and women for their empowerment for their better life. In Nashik we are running one community radio- Radio Vishwas 90.8 community radio.We covered 10 lakh listeners. Also we are running one library for students who want to do competitive exams, as well as for school students who do not have space and guide line in their home.we are organised several trg's for professtionals and for youth. on 7.1.16 we does one public prog for 16 to 35 age girls,2000 girls attend "Ananadincha Utsav 2016" throw we find 60 to 70 volunteers. Now we are engage to organised one prog. for 16 to 35 age group boys- Maitra Karwa 2016 on 9.8.16.
